5|$|Other {{nations have}} also been {{successful}} when hosting the tournament. Switzerland (quarter-finals 1954), Sweden (runners-up in 1958), Chile (third place in 1962), South Korea (fourth place in 2002), and Mexico (quarter-finals in 1970 and 1986) all have their best results when serving as hosts. So far, South Africa (2010) {{has been the only}} <b>host</b> <b>nation</b> to fail to advance beyond the first round.|$|E
